### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Track page view
POST http://localhost:4000/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "page_view",
  "path": "/pricing",
  "site": "marketing-site",
  "referrer": "https://google.com",
  "metadata": {
    "campaign": "spring-launch"
  }
}

### Dashboard metrics
GET http://localhost:4000/metrics/dashboard